quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,48,"Wama nureehim min ayatin illahiya akbaru min okhtiha waakhathnahum bilAAathabilaAAallahum yarjiAAoon"
  43,49,"Waqaloo ya ayyuha asahiruodAAu lana rabbaka bima AAahida AAindaka innanalamuhtadoon"
  43,50,"Falamma kashafna AAanhumualAAathaba itha hum yankuthoon"
  43,51,"Wanada firAAawnu fee qawmihi qalaya qawmi alaysa lee mulku misra wahathihial-anharu tajree min tahtee afala tubsiroon"
  43,52,"Am ana khayrun min hatha allatheehuwa maheenun wala yakadu yubeen"
  43,53,"Falawla olqiya AAalayhi aswiratun minthahabin aw jaa maAAahu almala-ikatumuqtarineen"
  43,54,"Fastakhaffa qawmahu faataAAoohuinnahum kanoo qawman fasiqeen"
  43,55,"Falamma asafoonaintaqamna minhum faaghraqnahum ajmaAAeen"
  43,56,"FajaAAalnahum salafan wamathalan lil-akhireen"
  43,57,"Walamma duriba ibnu maryamamathalan itha qawmuka minhu yasiddoon"
  43,58,"Waqaloo aalihatunakhayrun am huwa ma daraboohu laka illajadalan bal hum qawmun khasimoon"
  43,59,"In huwa illa AAabdun anAAamnaAAalayhi wajaAAalnahu mathalan libanee isra-eel"
  43,60,"Walaw nashao lajaAAalna minkummala-ikatan fee al-ardi yakhlufoon"
